{
  "description": "A high-angle, long-distance shot captures a large body of water, likely a bay or a sea, shimmering brightly under sunlight. The water\u2019s surface is heavily textured with light reflections, creating a dazzling, almost abstract pattern. A prominent wake of a boat or ship cuts through the water, extending from the lower center and curving towards the upper right. Silhouetted landmasses frame the water on both sides, dotted with trees and structures. The foreground features a dark, indistinct skyline of buildings and vegetation, providing a stark contrast to the bright water. The overall impression is one of expansive scale and the interplay of light and water.",
